<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1085</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yǒng bù piē xià nǐ, zhè shì yǔ nǐ lì de yuē.
 chūn xià qiū dōng rì rì yè yè, tā dōu péi bàn zhe.
 zhǔ bù huì wàng jì nǐ, zhè shì yǔ nǐ lì de yuē.
 tā bì bǎo shǒu nǐ shí fēn píng ān, suī rán nǐ jīng guò shuǐ huǒ.
 nǐ de yī shēng yǒu duō shǎo gù shì,
 yǒu xǐ yǒu yōu yǒu lèi yǒu gē. yǒu píng tǎn yǒu qū zhé,
 shí zài shì zhǔ de ài. jīn tiān hái huó zhe,
 zāi nán zhōng tā shì bì nán suǒ. zhǔ yǔ wǒ men yǒu yuē,
 jǐn guǎn dà shān néng nuó yí, hǎi shuǐ huì gàn hé.
 zhǔ zǒng bù piē xià nǐ hé wǒ, bù huì wàng jì nǐ hé wǒ.
 cǎi hóng wèi jì shí jià wèi zhèng, hái yǒu gǎn lǎn shù shàng de bái gē.
 zài zhǔ de yuē zhōng fàng shēng gāo gē. fàng shēng gāo gē.</lyrics>
<title>yuē 迦南1085</title>
</song>